394
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:52,009
<font color="yellow">Itu sebabnya aku hanya menua di sini.</font>

395
00:23:54,839 --> 00:23:55,880
<font color="yellow">Apa ini?</font>

396
00:23:55,910 --> 00:23:57,180
<font color="yellow">Kami membeli bunga ini karena indah.</font>

397
00:23:57,380 --> 00:23:59,380
