400
00:24:03,150 --> 00:24:05,890
<font color="yellow">Aku belum melihat musim semi.</font>

401
00:24:05,890 --> 00:24:07,490
<font color="yellow">Masih banyak hari tersisa.</font>

402
00:24:07,490 --> 00:24:08,759
<font color="yellow">Kapan?</font>

