404
00:24:16,230 --> 00:24:17,259
<font color="yellow">Masuk.</font>

405
00:24:20,869 --> 00:24:22,539
<font color="yellow">Apa Jaksa Jung ada?</font>

406
00:24:24,269 --> 00:24:25,710
<font color="yellow">- Hebat.
