407
00:24:26,569 --> 00:24:27,740
<font color="yellow">Bagus.</font>

408
00:24:35,019 --> 00:24:37,119
<font color="yellow">Kamu... siapa?</font>

409
00:24:37,250 --> 00:24:39,819
<font color="yellow">Aku Han Woo Tak. Aku kemari
