411
00:24:43,890 --> 00:24:44,890
<font color="yellow">Di sini.</font>

412
00:24:46,859 --> 00:24:48,430
<font color="yellow">Kalian membawa parfum?</font>

413
00:24:48,430 --> 00:24:50,299
<font color="yellow">- Tidak.
