414
00:24:52,529 --> 00:24:53,869
<font color="yellow">Sudah datang.</font>

415
00:24:54,700 --> 00:24:55,970
<font color="yellow">Musim seminya sudah datang.</font>

416
00:24:56,769 --> 00:24:58,470
<font color="yellow">"Pengacara Lee Yu Beom"</font>

417
00:25:03,740 --> 00:25:05,150
<font color="yellow">Astaga, aku kecewa.</font>

418
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:08,880
<font color="yellow">Kamu reporter yang kuhubungi
