451
00:27:07,640 --> 00:27:10,140
<font color="yellow">Pria yang tampan untuk polisi.</font>

452
00:27:10,470 --> 00:27:11,509
<font color="yellow">Benar.</font>

453
00:27:11,509 --> 00:27:13,970
<font color="yellow">Kenapa jaksa tidak
