455
00:27:16,710 --> 00:27:18,079
<font color="yellow">Kamu menyukainya, bukan?</font>

456
00:27:18,079 --> 00:27:21,180
<font color="yellow">Hanya sesaat. Sangat sesaat.</font>

457
00:27:21,579 --> 00:27:24,619
<font color="yellow">Kalian harus membaca surelnya.
