459
00:27:30,160 --> 00:27:31,559
<font color="yellow">Wajah tampan dan tinggi, mungkin?</font>

460
00:27:37,470 --> 00:27:39,269
<font color="yellow">Apa dia mendengar perkataanku dari tadi?</font>

461
00:27:39,269 --> 00:27:42,069
<font color="yellow">Ya, dari awal sampai akhir.</font>

462
00:27:42,069 --> 00:27:44,140
<font color="yellow">Astaga, apa yang kulakukan?</font>

463
00:27:44,140 --> 00:27:45,470
<font color="yellow">Dia sudah datang.</font>

464
00:27:45,940 --> 00:27:46,970
<font color="yellow">Kamu sudah datang.</font>

465
00:27:49,480 --> 00:27:52,109
<font color="yellow">Kamu datang awal. Kamu sudah makan siang?</font>

