483
00:28:44,900 --> 00:28:47,369
<font color="yellow">Kasus ini sangat mirip kasus Kang Dae Hee.</font>

484
00:28:47,470 --> 00:28:51,210
<font color="yellow">Dia jelas pelakunya, tapi hanya
